commit.message:
libgomp: Make nvptx helper routines self-contained.

	libgomp/
	* oacc-ptx.h (GOACC_INTERNAL_PTX): Add GOACC_tid, GOACC_ntid,
	GOACC_ctaid, and GOACC_nctaid routines.

Co-Authored-By: Cesar Philippidis <cesar@codesourcery.com>

From-SVN: r220768
